milestones.description: Ryan ten Doeschate has broken the record for most sixes (11) in ODIs for NED, going past van Bunge's 9

stories.title: ten Doeschate stars in Netherlands win
stories.subTitle: Netherlands v Bermuda, 2nd ODI, Amstelveen
stories.summary: While Thursday's game was washed out because of heavy rain, today's was restricted to 40 overs-a-side and Netherlands chased down their revised total of 174 with 23 balls to spare
